{"tid":559793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【神扯片】女子鑽入安檢機　極致透視！全部看光光","createTime":"2018-02-13T13:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T23:25:36.000Z","uid":84436,"like":120,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"039dc58cbe3fe40bb443210920aa3ba1cc958531","tid":559793,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:33:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180213/1297940\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297940&d=juZNQ8TWd%2FZKTWwpyWEy8mi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=42bbf620\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180213%2F1297940&h=08607c4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180213/1297940</a><br />\n<br />\n傻眼！中國一名女子前天到廣東東莞市要搭車，因為擔心隨身包包內的財物遺失，竟然連人帶包進入安檢機，結果顯示器就出現人形透視圖，骨骼被照得一清二楚，令安檢人員傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n據《梨視頻》報導，2月11日晚上6時許，一名女乘客的行李箱通過安檢後，被提醒隨身包包也必須放到安檢機輸送帶檢查，女子擔心包包裡財物不見，便連人帶包直接鑽入安檢機一起檢查。報導中提醒，安檢機內輻射較大，對人體有一定傷害。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）"},{"pid":"6eab75fbdf61fe5effda8a3ceef4e62746bdd910","tid":559793,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b53d9f30707c8ac2a5a1ae1bb015f32145d114b","tid":559793,"uid":116143,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:39:56.000Z","msg":"大媽好撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e71597d127c88ca23b7c424769053ee3c467ec","tid":559793,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6eab75fbdf61fe5effda8a3ceef4e62746bdd910","tid":559793,"uid":10788,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:34:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T13:40:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <